The Beijing 2022 Winter Olympics torch relay, on the second day, passed through the Badaling section of the Great Wall of China. The torch relay for the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympics is scheduled from February 2 to 4. Follow CGTN reporters to see what it is like to relay the Olympic flame on the Great Wall.  Reporters: Liu Xiaoxian, Liang Si Camera: Ding Zhiyang, Shi Chan Cover photo designer: Feng Yuan Copy editor: Nadeem Gill Chief Editor: Chen Ran Supervisor: Zhang Shilei